          "text": "This 4K documentary is such a visual masterpiece! Aside from the main island, it took us to many stunning remote islands like the Kerama Islands, Miyako with its long sea bridges, or the ancient Taketomi Island with its water buffalo carts. If you had the chance to pack your bags and go tomorrow, which island would be your very first stop?",
